# Each package has its own .env.example:
#
#   packages/backend/.env.example   — Next.js API backend (Supabase, OpenAI, etc.)
#   apps/admin-ui/.env.example      — Admin UI (NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL)
#   apps/example-consumer/          — Angular env files (src/environments/environment.ts)
#
# There are no root-level environment variables.
